(4183, 714, 'So why did a Quetz cross the road?', 'I don''t know, why did I?', 15, '+1 Riddles, +1 focus, +1 wisdom'),
(4184, 716, 'Maybe here?', '* lifts a very heavy rock to find what #he is looking for.', 9, '+1 strength'),
